    {
      "id": "PopularPost342100",
      "post_content": "Gave it 4/5 because it is brilliant at what it does.  \n  \nHowever, personally I think it is overpowered. Thinking of [Day of Judgment](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Day of Judgment ) and [Wrath of God](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wrath of God), those cost 4 mana; and those I think are too cheap. The effects are so strong that they should be more expensive; especially when one thinks how much creatures cost.  \n  \nOh btw: This card is probably the best anti-Theros there is, with Theros focusing on enchantment-everything.  \n  \nNow... Where's my Avacyn when I need her....",
      "posted_by": "MortisAngelus",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost342100\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_post\">Gave it 4/5 because it is brilliant at what it does.<br/><br/>However, personally I think it is overpowered. Thinking of <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Day of Judgment \" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Day of Judgment \">Day of Judgment </a>and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Wrath of God\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wrath of God\">Wrath of God</a>, those cost 4 mana; and those I think are too cheap. The effects are so strong that they should be more expensive; especially when one thinks how much creatures cost.<br/><br/>Oh btw: This card is probably the best anti-Theros there is, with Theros focusing on enchantment-everything.<br/><br/>Now... Where's my Avacyn when I need her....</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '342100'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy94967\">MortisAngelus</span>\r\n                                (9/21/2013 6:10:10 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_c