      "id": "PopularPost192442",
      "post_content": "I don't get all the hate; this isn't overpowered. [Day of Judgment](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Day of Judgment) isn't broken because it wiped out five of your creatures. And [Kor Firewalker](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Kor Firewalker) isn't broken just because it kills a red deck dead. Back to Nature is way more situational than either of these.",
